column5: I thought it was Anthony Bourdain & Larry the Cable Guys brother.

At a recent camp owners function I met someone who I've only known from WC. Of course from his many long winded posts and off the wall points of view, I had formed an image in my mind of who this person might be. Let's say I was surprised that my mental image was way off the mark. Anybody care to guess who's who in this picture?
Fisherman Ted I'll pick up my luxurious gift from the lodge gift shop in June. PjShorthorn
The orvis fleece is a dead giveaway. As for the other guy, I hadn't realized Ted Kaczynski was out of jail.
This......is.....excellent!!!!!! But how in the h*** did he sneak across the border??????
Two very good looking dudes. I too am surprised every year they let me in..... -FT
http://i95.photobucket.com/albums/l1...su0b4isj4.jpeghttp://i95.photobucket.com/albums/l1...sgxwey7eb.jpegWhat do I win?Sent from my iPhone using Tapatalk

I was expecting Ted to be much taller, possibly wearing a tie, and sprouting $100 bills (US of course because of the convenience factor). As it was I had to chase him away from sneaking half empty wine glasses off the table. I finally just bought him drinks for the rest of the night so he wouldn't embarrass himself further....... He did say caviar prices for the camp were way up this year.....By the way all winning guesses are eligible for a free cold one in the fish house at VBL. I'm also planning on taking Ted up on his offer to stop by his lodge for happy hour. I'm sure when he said this he was referring to all his WC friends and acquaintances.

Uuuummmm, Gord ? I don't know how to break it to you, but Ted has offered me a full week's stay at his place since I was the first to guess his identity correctly. How about you just bring the beer to the happy hour at Ted's place ? Since you will more than likely not want to drive home after the social, you can bunk in my cabin. The washrooms have large clawfoot tubs ,from what I understand , so you should be able to get at least two thirds of your Sasquatch size body into the tub. PjShorthorn
